## üí° HTML Project Ideas

| Project              | Concepts Used                           |
| -------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| Personal Portfolio   | Semantic HTML, Forms, Links, Images     |
| Resume Webpage       | Lists, Tables, Typography               |
| Product Landing Page | Forms, Multimedia, Responsiveness       |
| Blog Layout          | Articles, Sections, Metadata            |
| Survey Form          | Input fields, Validation, Accessibility |

